S.FORM: kaljavevean i prague (kai nua seczech: Pražské jaro; kai nua seslovak: Pražská jar) mavan a ka pidjalan a qadaw tua kiqaung sa semucaqev tua pulitiks tazua maqepuqepu a tjuruvu a sikataqaljan a seczech. na patagilj tiamadju ka napiniliq ti Alexander Dubček a masan sangasangasan a kisanpusaladj tua namalaing tua kinateveteveljan nua Communist i Czechoslovakia ka i sikamasanlimalj a qadaw i 1 a qiljas i 1968 a cavilj. na semekez tiamadju ka i 21 a qadav i 8 qiljas i 1968 a cavilj ayatua na tjaljuzuain a paselapai nua kinateveteveljan nua soviet imaza i czech. kinipalaing ni Dubček aicu a kaljavevean i prague. saka ulja kiquang timadju tu venala a sikataqaljan a sezech kipaqenetj kisuamadju.

kaljavevean i pragoe (kai noa seczech: Pražské jaro; kai noa seslovak: Pražská jar) mavan a ka pidjalan a qadaw toa kiqaong sa semocaqev toa politiks tazoa maqepoqepo a tjorovo a sikataqaljan a seczech. na patagilj tiamadjo ka napiniliq ti Alexander Dobček a masan sangasangasan a kisanposaladj toa namalaing toa kinateveteveljan noa Commonist i Czechoslovakia ka i sikamasanlimalj a qadaw i 1 a qiljas i 1968 a cavilj. na semekez tiamadjo ka i 21 a qadav i 8 qiljas i 1968 a cavilj ayatoa na tjaljozoain a paselapai noa kinateveteveljan noa soviet imaza i czech. kinipalaing ni Dobček aico a kaljavevean i pragoe. saka olja kiqoang timadjo to venala a sikataqaljan a sezech kipaqenetj kisoamadjo.
